        <name>7.1.4.2 Addition and Subtraction of Matrices</name>
        <questiontext>&lt;p class="HELM_exercise"&gt;Exercise&lt;/p&gt;
For the following matrices find \(A+B,\ A-B,\ B-A,\ 2A\):&amp;nbsp;&lt;p&gt;\[A = {@mat1@} \text{ and } B = {@mat2@}.\]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol class="HELM_parts"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;div&gt;\(A+B = \) [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]][[feedback:prt1]]&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;div&gt;\(A-B = \) [[input:ans2]] [[validation:ans2]][[feedback:prt2]]&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;div&gt;\(B-A = \) [[input:ans3]] [[validation:ans3]][[feedback:prt3]]&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;div&gt;\(2A = \)&amp;nbsp; [[input:ans4]] [[validation:ans4]][[feedback:prt4]]&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;</questiontext>
        <questiontextformat>1</questiontextformat>
        <generalfeedback>&lt;p&gt;We are give the matrices&lt;/p&gt;
\[A = {@mat1@} \quad \text{and} \quad B = {@mat2@},\]
&lt;p&gt;and are asked to find the following.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Recall that addition, subtraction and scalar multiplication of matrices is performed element-wise.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol class="HELM_parts"&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
        \[A + B = {@mat1@} + {@mat2@} = {@sumsteps@} = {@ta1@}\]
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
        \[A - B = {@mat1@} - {@mat2@} = {@substeps1@} = {@ta2@}\]
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
        \[B - A = {@mat2@} - {@mat1@} = {@substeps2@} = {@ta3@}\]
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
        \[2A = 2 {@mat1@} = {@mulsteps@} = {@ta4@}\]
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;</generalfeedback>
